			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">聚流</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="435" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">聚流力场：半径12m范围内重力减弱，跳起时减速<span color="#ffdfbf">45%</span><span>；同时先驱阵列自身</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+65%</span><span>全抗。 </span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
