		<RichText x="1411" y="799" width="442" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当先驱阵列陷入冻结状态时，若冻结状态被<span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">碎冰</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">融化</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">结晶</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">扩散</span><span>等反应解除，则将立即中断「聚流力场」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
